{
  "stem": "1858.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Had the people of my hometown known what was to follow-- had they had an idea, even-- they would have risen further back when we were still united, when our leaders were among us, when the strength was there.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But after all, this was the 20th century.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who could even believe that the Nazis, the German people, the highly cultural German nation, the people who are so highly educated-- not barbarians from a primitive, backward country-- but Germany-- with the best-educated scientists, with the Wagner music, with Beethoven's, and all that-- who would believe that there was a definite plan at work?",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, when we found out where that-- about the death of my brother-- I cannot tell you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I cannot explain what a terrible shock this was to us, especially to my father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, in the Jewish religion, it is the son who says the kaddish, or the prayer, after his father dies.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Can you imagine how difficult it must have been for my father to have to say the kaddish after his one and only son?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I can't imagine how he could endure that pain, how painful that must have been to him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was then, in December-- of September, 1939, that I realized that life will never be the same for me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But of course, little did I know that this was only the beginning of things to come.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall, because that wasn't immediately.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because he didn't have a regular burial place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't even know exactly where.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't remember if they did or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But if-- if that was required, I'm sure that they did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I did not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't remember sitting shiva because in school--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went and returned to school.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
